{"tid":488140,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"火影收東九龍黑幫皮","createTime":"2017-12-03T12:12:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-03T12:47:32.000Z","uid":389,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6c97bac996d1ea9f47c9368c3837abc64977e4ed","tid":488140,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T12:12:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/03/201214_ee75ac235d8c5fb8be8b3f16812b38fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F03%2F201214_ee75ac235d8c5fb8be8b3f16812b38fd.jpg&h=30001117&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n東九龍警區刑事總部採取代號「火影行動」的大型反三合會行動，打擊黑社會非法活動，拘捕120人。行動聯同黃大仙、秀茂坪、觀塘及將軍澳四個警區，周五（1日）起一連三日派出300多人，根據線報及深入調查，以打擊一個活躍於東九龍的非法組織及其收入來源。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/港聞/138414/警方-臥底-滲黑幫搜證-一連三日-火影行動-除三害拘120人\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2F138414%2F%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9-%E8%87%A5%E5%BA%95-%E6%BB%B2%E9%BB%91%E5%B9%AB%E6%90%9C%E8%AD%89-%E4%B8%80%E9%80%A3%E4%B8%89%E6%97%A5-%E7%81%AB%E5%BD%B1%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95-%E9%99%A4%E4%B8%89%E5%AE%B3%E6%8B%98120%E4%BA%BA&d=rKcJJVa6SMWng0bfshvUrsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=6dc101f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/港聞/138414/警方-臥底-滲黑幫搜證-一連三日-火影行動-除三害拘120人</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/03/201203_af3d4a2fa0b3e4949e9d66d48d8f54c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F03%2F201203_af3d4a2fa0b3e4949e9d66d48d8f54c8.jpg&h=1d230e2f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2acdf7d657c0eb00d674fcdfe1db3fbcf19c53c3","tid":488140,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T12:13:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/138414\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F138414&d=rKcJJVa6SMWng0bfshvUrsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=737104f2\" data-auto-link 